title: Prep Softball: North Bend handles Reedsport, 10-1
title_page: Prep Softball: North Bend handles Reedsport, 10-1
maintext:
NORTH BEND — Reedsport dropped a 10-1 nonleague decision to North Bend Friday in high school softball.
The 4A Bulldogs evened their season record at 1-1, while the 2A Brave fell to 2-1. No details were provided by Reedsport.
